ntiates through its order book model (vs AMM), millisecond latency, capital efficiency (<1.5% of principal), and focus on rate trading as a standalone primitive rather than embedded in yield tokenization.	https://x.com/supernovalabs_?s=21&t=nNmmq43RV9J-8fLg3xTwXA	reaching_out	{"Interest Rate Derivatives",DeFi,"Onchain Order Book","Fixed Rate Lending"}	\N	2026-03-20 09:35:00.173705	https://www.supernova.vision/	\N	https://x.com/SupernovaLabs_	\N	1e9bf641-c93c-4629-906a-f50db9050164	Perpetuals/Derivatives	0	\N	\N	\N	f	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
